<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MyCarReferral — Earn Money Referring Car Buyers</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
body { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; color:#1E293B; background:#f8fafc; }
header { background:#1E293B; padding:16px 20px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; }
.logo { color:#00C851; font-size:20px; font-weight:800; text-decoration:none; }
.logo span { color:white; font-weight:400; }
.header-btn { background:#00C851; color:#1E293B; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:8px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; }
.hero { background:#1E293B; padding:80px 20px; text-align:center; }
.hero h1 { font-size:42px; font-weight:800; color:white; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:16px; max-width:600px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; }
.hero h1 span { color:#00C851; }
.hero p { font-size:18px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width:500px; margin:0 auto 40px; line-height:1.6; }
.hero-btns { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.btn-primary { background:#00C851; color:#1E293B; padding:16px 32px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:800; font-size:16px; }
.btn-secondary { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color:white; padding:16px 32px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:700; font-size:16px; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
.section { padding:60px 20px; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; }
.section-title { font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#1E293B; text-align:center; margin-bottom:8px; }
.section-sub { font-size:16px; color:#64748B; text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px; }
.steps { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap:24px; }
.step { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:28px; text-align:center; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
.step-num { background:#00C851; color:#1E293B; width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:800; font-size:16px; margin:0 auto 16px; }
.step h3 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#1E293B; margin-bottom:8px; }
.step p { font-size:13px; color:#64748B; line-height:1.5; }
.business-section { background:#1E293B; padding:60px 20px; }
.business-inner { max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; }
.business-inner .section-title { color:white; }
.business-inner .section-sub { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.business-cards { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:20px; }
.business-card { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius:16px; padding:24px; }
.business-card .icon { font-size:32px; margin-bottom:12px; }
.business-card h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:white; margin-bottom:8px; }
.business-card p { font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height:1.6; }
.templates-section { padding:60px 20px; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; }
.template-cards { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr)); gap:20px; }
.template-card { background:white; border-radius:16px; padding:24px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); border:1px solid #E2E8F0; }
.template-card .tag { font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#00C851; margin-bottom:8px; }
.template-card p { font-size:14px; color:#475569; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:16px; }
.copy-btn { background:#1E293B; color:white; border:none; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:8px; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; width:100%; }
.copy-btn:hover { background:#00C851; color:#1E293B; }
.cta-section { background:#00C851; padding:60px 20px; text-align:center; }
.cta-section h2 { font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:#1E293B; margin-bottom:12px; }
.cta-section p { font-size:16px; color:rgba(30,41,59,0.7); margin-bottom:32px; }
.cta-section a { background:#1E293B; color:white; padding:16px 40px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:800; font-size:16px; }
footer { background:#1E293B; padding:24px 20px; text-align:center; }
footer p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size:12px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a href="/" class="logo"><span>My</span>CarReferral</a>
  <a href="/login" class="header-btn">Check My Referrals</a>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Earn Money by Sending <span>Car Buyers</span> to the Right Rep.</h1>
  <p>No license needed. No desk. No boss. Just refer people you know — and get paid when they buy.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="/login" class="btn-primary">Check My Referrals →</a>
    <a href="#how" class="btn-secondary">How It Works</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section" id="how">
  <div class="section-title">Simple. Transparent. Profitable.</div>
  <div class="section-sub">Four steps between you and your first gift.</div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <h3>Know someone buying a car?</h3>
      <p>A friend, family member, coworker — anyone shopping for a vehicle.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <h3>Send them to your rep</h3>
      <p>Share your rep's link or submit their info directly from your dashboard.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <h3>They buy a car</h3>
      <p>Your rep closes the deal. You get notified the moment it happens.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <h3>You receive a Thank You gift</h3>
      <p>Every closed deal earns you a gift from the dealership. No limits on how many you earn.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="business-section">
  <div class="business-inner">
    <div class="section-title">Run Your Own Referral Business</div>
    <div class="section-sub">MyCarReferral.com is more than a tracking tool — it's a business platform.</div>
    <div class="business-cards">
      <div class="business-card">
        <div class="icon">📲</div>
        <h3>Post. Refer. Earn.</h3>
        <p>Use our premade social media templates to post on Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp. Every person who clicks your link and buys is money in your pocket.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="business-card">
        <div class="icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Track Every Referral</h3>
        <p>Your personal dashboard shows every buyer you sent, their status in real time, and every gift you've earned. Full transparency, always.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="business-card">
        <div class="icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>Work Multiple Dealerships</h3>
        <p>Build relationships with reps at different dealerships. Every new rep connection is a new income stream — all tracked in one place.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="templates-section">
  <div class="section-title">Ready-to-Post Social Templates</div>
  <div class="section-sub">Copy, paste, and post. Your link is already built in.</div>
  <div class="template-cards">
    <div class="template-card">
      <div class="tag">Facebook / Instagram</div>
      <p>🚗 Know someone looking for a car? I work with an amazing sales rep who makes the process easy — no pressure, no runaround. Send me their name and I'll connect them. If they buy, I receive a Thank You gift! 🎁 Drop a comment or DM me.</p>
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText(this, '🚗 Know someone looking for a car? I work with an amazing sales rep who makes the process easy — no pressure, no runaround. Send me their name and I\'ll connect them. If they buy, I receive a Thank You gift! 🎁 Drop a comment or DM me.')">Copy This Template</button>
    </div>
    <div class="template-card">
      <div class="tag">WhatsApp / Text</div>
      <p>Hey! I've been referring people to a great car salesperson and getting rewarded for it. If you or anyone you know needs a car, let me know — I'll connect you and get paid if it works out. Win-win! 🙌</p>
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText(this, 'Hey! I\'ve been referring people to a great car salesperson and getting rewarded for it. If you or anyone you know needs a car, let me know — I\'ll connect you and get paid if it works out. Win-win! 🙌')">Copy This Template</button>
    </div>
    <div class="template-card">
      <div class="tag">LinkedIn / Professional</div>
      <p>💼 I've partnered with a trusted auto sales professional to help connect buyers with the right vehicle. If you or someone in your network is in the market, reach out — I receive a referral gift for every successful purchase.</p>
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyText(this, '💼 I\'ve partnered with a trusted auto sales professional to help connect buyers with the right vehicle. If you or someone in your network is in the market, reach out — I receive a referral gift for every successful purchase.')">Copy This Template</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
  <h2>Already a Member?</h2>
  <p>Check your referrals, submit new buyers, and track your gifts.</p>
  <a href="/login">Log Into My Dashboard →</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 MyCarReferral. Powered by CarsInStock. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

<script>
function copyText(btn, text) {
  navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() {
    var orig = btn.textContent;
    btn.textContent = '✅ Copied!';
    btn.style.background = '#00C851';
    btn.style.color = '#1E293B';
    setTimeout(function() {
      btn.textContent = orig;
      btn.style.background = '#1E293B';
      btn.style.color = 'white';
    }, 2000);
  });
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
